NimNamedClientSession
public class NimClientSession
extends NimSession

This class is used for sending requests / receiving responses from some other party. Mark the difference between the NimClientSession and NimServerSession and that a NimClientSession may turn into a NimServerSession

setLocalAddress

public static void setLocalAddress(String localAddress)
                            throws Exception
Set the specific local address that sockets will bind to. If not specified, the NIMBUS_LOCAL_IP system property or environment variable will be used. If not specified by either setLocalAddress or NIMBUS_LOCAL_IP, the system will pick a local address to bind to.

Parameters:
localAddress - The local address that sockets will bind to.
